    <item>
      <title>Policies</title>
      <link>https://www.willowandsagefarms.com/policies/</link>
      <pubDate>Tue, 27 Jan 2026 23:55:01 -0800</pubDate>
      <guid>https://www.willowandsagefarms.com/policies/</guid>
      <description>&lt;div class=&#34;policies&#34; style=&#34;background: black; padding-top: 2rem;&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;p style=&#34; max-width: 800px; margin: auto;&#34;&gt;&#xA;  These policies are in place to protect both our customers and our small-batch bakery. &lt;br&gt; &#xA;  By placing an order, you agree to the following terms.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;details&gt;&#xA;    &lt;summary&gt;&#xA;        Ordering Policy&#xA;    &lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;    &lt;div&gt;&#xA;        &lt;ul&gt;&#xA;            &lt;li&gt;All orders must be placed through our website, direct invoice, or approved sales channel.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;            &lt;li&gt;Orders are confirmed only once payment is received in full, unless otherwise stated in writing.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;            &lt;li&gt;We operate on a limited production schedule. Once an order is confirmed, it is added to our baking calendar and ingredients are allocated specifically for you.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;            &lt;li&gt;Order deadlines will be clearly stated for pre-orders, markets, and special items. Late orders may not be accepted.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;      &lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;/details&gt;&#xA;&lt;details&gt;&#xA;    &lt;summary&gt;&#xA;        Custom &amp; Special Orders&#xA;    &lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;    &lt;div&gt;&#xA;        &lt;ul&gt;&#xA;            &lt;li&gt;Custom orders include (but are not limited to) cookie cakes, custom sizing, special flavors, or decorative finishes.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;            &lt;li&gt;Design inspiration photos are accepted as references only. Final products may vary slightly due to the handmade nature of baking.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;            &lt;li&gt;Once a custom order is approved and paid for, it cannot be cancelled or refunded.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;      &lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;/details&gt;&#xA;&lt;details&gt;&#xA;    &lt;summary&gt;&#xA;        Pricing &amp; Payments&#xA;    &lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;    &lt;div&gt;&#xA;        &lt;ul&gt;&#xA;            &lt;li&gt;All prices are listed in CAD and are subject to change without notice.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;            &lt;li&gt;Payment methods accepted will be clearly stated at checkout or on invoices.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;            &lt;li&gt;Taxes will be applied where required by law.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;      &lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;/details&gt;&#xA;&lt;details&gt;&#xA;    &lt;summary&gt;&#xA;        Cancellation &amp; Refund Policy&#xA;    &lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;    &lt;div&gt;&#xA;        &lt;ul&gt;&#xA;            &lt;li&gt;Due to the perishable nature of baked goods, &lt;strong&gt;all sales are final&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;            &lt;li&gt;We do not offer refunds or credits for change of mind, no-shows, or failure to pick up orders.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;            &lt;li&gt;If there is an issue with your order, you must notify us within 24 hours of pickup or delivery, with clear photos of the product and original packaging.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;      &lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;/details&gt;&#xA;&lt;details&gt;&#xA;    &lt;summary&gt;&#xA;        AI, Photo Manipulation &amp; Fraud Prevention Policy&#xA;    &lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;    &lt;div&gt;&#xA;        &lt;ul&gt;&#xA;            &lt;li&gt;Due to the rise in AI image generation, photo editing, and digital manipulation, &lt;strong&gt;no refunds or replacements will be issued without the return of the original product&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;            &lt;li&gt;Claims based solely on photos will not be accepted.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;            &lt;li&gt;Returned items must be substantially intact and returned within 24 hours of delivery or pickup, unless otherwise agreed upon in writing.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;            &lt;li&gt;We reserve the right to refuse refunds or replacements if fraud or misrepresentation is suspected.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;      &lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;/details&gt;&#xA;&lt;details&gt;&#xA;    &lt;summary&gt;&#xA;        Delivery Policy&#xA;    &lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;    &lt;div&gt;&#xA;        &lt;ul&gt;&#xA;            &lt;li&gt;Delivery areas, days, and fees are listed on our website or order page.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;            &lt;li&gt;Customers are responsible for providing accurate delivery information.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;            &lt;li&gt;We are not responsible for delayed, missed, or failed deliveries due to incorrect addresses, lack of access, or unattended drop-off locations.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;            &lt;li&gt;Once an order is marked as delivered, responsibility transfers to the customer.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;      &lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;/details&gt;&#xA;&lt;details&gt;&#xA;    &lt;summary&gt;&#xA;        Product Handling &amp; Storage&#xA;    &lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;    &lt;div&gt;&#xA;        &lt;ul&gt;&#xA;            &lt;li&gt;We are not responsible for product quality once items have been improperly stored, handled, or transported by the customer.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;            &lt;li&gt;Storage instructions are provided for best quality and food safety and should be followed carefully.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;        &lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;/details&gt;&#xA;&lt;details&gt;&#xA;    &lt;summary&gt;&#xA;        Allergens &amp; Food Safety&#xA;    &lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;    &lt;div&gt;&#xA;        &lt;ul&gt;&#xA;            &lt;li&gt;Our kitchen handles common allergens including (but not limited to) wheat, gluten, dairy, eggs, and nuts.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;            &lt;li&gt;We cannot guarantee an allergen-free environment.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;            &lt;li&gt;Customers are responsible for reviewing ingredient lists and asking questions before ordering.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;      &lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;/details&gt;&#xA;&lt;details&gt;&#xA;    &lt;summary&gt;&#xA;        Market &amp; Event Sales&#xA;    &lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;    &lt;div&gt;&#xA;        &lt;ul&gt;&#xA;            &lt;li&gt;All market and event sales are final.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;            &lt;li&gt;We cannot hold items without prior arrangement.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;            &lt;li&gt;Product availability is first-come, first-served.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;      &lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;/details&gt;&#xA;&lt;details&gt;&#xA;    &lt;summary&gt;&#xA;        Right to Refuse Service&#xA;    &lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;    &lt;div&gt;&#xA;        &lt;ul&gt;&#xA;            &lt;li&gt;We reserve the right to refuse service to anyone for abusive behavior, harassment, attempted fraud, or violation of these policies.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;      &lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;/details&gt;&#xA;&lt;details&gt;&#xA;    &lt;summary&gt;&#xA;        Policy Updates&#xA;    &lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;    &lt;div&gt;&#xA;        &lt;ul&gt;&#xA;            &lt;li&gt;These policies are subject to change at any time without prior notice.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;            &lt;li&gt;The most current version will always be available upon request or on our website.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;      &lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;/details&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/div&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Contact Us</title>
      <link>https://www.willowandsagefarms.com/contact/</link>
      <pubDate>Fri, 28 Nov 2025 20:11:35 -0800</pubDate>
      <guid>https://www.willowandsagefarms.com/contact/</guid>
      <description>&lt;section class=&#34;contact-section&#34; style=&#34;max-width: 80vw; margin: 0 auto&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;p style=&#34;margin-top:0;&#34;&gt;&#xA;    We love hearing from customers, big and small. &lt;br&gt;&#xA;    Whether you want to place an order, ask about ingredients, arrange pickup, or talk wholesale, send us a message and we will get back to you.&#xA;  &lt;/p&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div style=&#34;display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr;gap:1.25rem;margin-top:1.5rem;&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;!-- Contact Details --&gt;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;contact-details&#34; style=&#34;color: #000000;background:#ffffff;padding:1rem;border-radius:10px;box-shadow:0 2px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.04);&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &lt;h2 class=&#34;remove-style&#34;&gt;Email:&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;      &lt;p style=&#34;font-size:1.6rem; margin:0 0 0.75rem 0&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;a href=&#34;mailto:willowandsagefarms@gmail.com&#34; style=&#34;color:#000000;word-break:break-all&#34;&gt;willowandsagefarms@gmail.com&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;      &lt;/p&gt;&#xA;      &lt;br&gt;&#xA;      &lt;h2 style=&#34;margin:0 0 0.5rem 0&#34;&gt;Socials:&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;      &lt;p style=&#34;margin:0 0 0.75rem 0&#34;&gt;&#xA;        Instagram and Facebook: &lt;strong&gt;@willowandsagefarms&lt;/strong&gt;&#xA;      &lt;/p&gt;&#xA;      &lt;br&gt;&#xA;      &lt;h2 style=&#34;margin:0 0 0.5rem 0&#34;&gt;Delivery&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;      &lt;ul style=&#34;list-style:none;margin:0 0 0 1rem;padding:0;color:#333;&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;li style=&#34;margin-bottom:1rem&#34;&gt;Local delivery available across the Sunshine Coast. &lt;br&gt; Free delivery in Sechelt. Flat fee of $5 for other areas in the Sunshine Coast.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;        &lt;li style=&#34;margin-bottom:1rem&#34;&gt;We bake Friday and pack orders for Saturday pickup and delivery. For custom orders and delivery times please use our contact form below.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;      &lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &lt;!-- Contact Form --&gt;&#xA;    &lt;form class=&#34;contact-form&#34; action=&#34;mailto:willowandsagefarms@gmail.com&#34; method=&#34;post&#34; enctype=&#34;text/plain&#34; style=&#34;display:flex;flex-direction:column; align-items: center; justify-content: center; color:black;background:white;padding:1rem;border-radius:10px;box-shadow:0 2px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.04);&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &lt;h2 style=&#34;font-size:1.1rem;margin:0 0 0.75rem 0&#34;&gt;Send us a message&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;      &lt;label for=&#34;name&#34; style=&#34;display:block;margin-bottom:0.4rem;font-weight:600&#34;&gt;Name&lt;/label&gt;&#xA;      &lt;input id=&#34;name&#34; name=&#34;Name&#34; type=&#34;text&#34; required style=&#34;width:80%;padding:0.6rem;border:1px solid #e6e6e6;border-radius:6px;margin-bottom:0.75rem&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &lt;label for=&#34;email&#34; style=&#34;display:block;margin-bottom:0.4rem;font-weight:600&#34;&gt;Email&lt;/label&gt;&#xA;      &lt;input id=&#34;email&#34; name=&#34;Email&#34; type=&#34;email&#34; required style=&#34;width:80%;padding:0.6rem;border:1px solid #e6e6e6;border-radius:6px;margin-bottom:0.75rem&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &lt;label for=&#34;order-type&#34; style=&#34;display:block;margin-bottom:0.4rem;font-weight:600&#34;&gt;Reason for contact&lt;/label&gt;&#xA;      &lt;select id=&#34;order-type&#34; name=&#34;Reason&#34; style=&#34;width:80%;padding:0.6rem;border:1px solid #e6e6e6;border-radius:6px;margin-bottom:0.75rem&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;option&gt;General question&lt;/option&gt;&#xA;        &lt;option&gt;Place an order&lt;/option&gt;&#xA;        &lt;option&gt;Pickup or delivery&lt;/option&gt;&#xA;        &lt;option&gt;Wholesale / event&lt;/option&gt;&#xA;        &lt;option&gt;Other&lt;/option&gt;&#xA;      &lt;/select&gt;&#xA;      &lt;label for=&#34;message&#34; style=&#34;display:block;margin-bottom:0.4rem;font-weight:600&#34;&gt;Message&lt;/label&gt;&#xA;      &lt;textarea id=&#34;message&#34; name=&#34;Message&#34; rows=&#34;6&#34;  required style=&#34;resize: none;width:80%;padding:0.6rem;border:1px solid #e6e6e6;border-radius:6px;margin-bottom:0.75rem&#34; placeholder=&#34;Tell us what you need, preferred pickup or delivery date, and any dietary notes&#34;&gt;&lt;/textarea&gt;&#xA;      &lt;button type=&#34;submit&#34; style=&#34;display:inline-block;padding:0.6rem 1rem;border-radius:8px;border:none;background:#2a7f4f;color:white;font-weight:700;cursor:pointer&#34;&gt;Send message&lt;/button&gt;&#xA;      &lt;small style=&#34;display:block;margin-top:0.6rem;color:#666&#34;&gt;If the form does not work for you, please email &lt;a href=&#34;mailto:willowandsagefarms@gmail.com&#34;&gt;willowandsagefarms@gmail.com&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/small&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/form&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;/section&gt;</description>
